## ğŸ” Overview

HypnoNeuroToken (HNT) is a utility token powering the **HypnoNeuro gamified healing platform**. It supports the decentralized reward system for:

- Player progress in therapeutic rooms  
- NFT-based milestones (Mind Mastery NFTs)  
- Practitioner payments and premium services  
- Discounts and token-based session booking  

Built using OpenZeppelin's secure ERC-20 contract structure, HNT includes:

- ğŸ” `Ownable` â€” restricts minting/burning/pausing to the platform owner  
- ğŸ”„ `ERC20Pausable` â€” lets the contract pause all transfers when needed  
- ğŸ”¨ Minting: Controlled token creation  
- ğŸ”¥ Burning: Allows token removal by users  
- â¸ Pausing: Freezes transfers in emergencies  

